---
import Container from "../components/Container.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PrimaryArrowButton from "../components/buttons/PrimaryArrowButton.astro";

---

<!-- Page Layout -->
<Layout title="About Us">
    <Container>
        <!-- About -->
        <div class="max-w-5xl px-6 pt-6 lg:pt-14 pb-12 sm:px-6 mx-auto">
            <div class="max-w-14xl mt-12">

                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="space-y-5 md:space-y-6">
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl dark:text-white">Who Are We?</h1>

                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        At Crab Labs, we provide precision electrical and software engineering services for clients who demand excellence. We’re a small, focused team of experienced engineers who choose our projects carefully. When we commit, we go all in.
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        We specialize in developing robust, production-ready systems across a range of industries, including biomedical devices, industrial automation, e-mobility platforms, and advanced consumer electronics. Whether you're launching a new product or refining a critical subsystem, we bring deep technical expertise and relentless attention to detail.
                    </p>

                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl dark:text-white">What Sets Us Apart?</h1>
                    
                    <ul>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white"><b>Expert Engineers Only:</b> No handoffs to junior staff. Every project is executed by seasoned professionals.</li>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white"><b>Selective by Design: </b> We only take on work where we can deliver exceptional results.</li>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white"><b>Disciplinary Capability:</b> From full-stack software to power electronics, we connect the dots. </li>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white"><b>Transparency & Trust:</b> Clear communication, honest timelines, and reliable delivery every time.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                    We don’t aim to be the biggest firm. We aim to be the best development partner you’ve ever worked with.
                    </p>

                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl dark:text-white">What Can We Do?</h1>

                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        Our passionate and talented multi-disciplinary team can take on projects in nearly all domains.
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold md:text-2xl dark:text-white">Design</h2>
                    
                    <ul>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- <b>Electronics</b>: Power, Digital, Analog, and Mixed Signal Systems</li>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- <b>Software/Firmware</b>: Embedded (IoT), Web, Desktop, and Mobile Applications</li>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- <b>Mechanical</b>: Plastic and Metal Assemblies</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold md:text-2xl dark:text-white"> Manufacturing</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        Our state of the art facility enables us to assemble our own electronics as well as manufacture a bevy of supporting components and enclosures. We produce all limited-run prototypes in house as much as possible.

                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        For items we can't build in house, we have a large network of foreign and domestic manufacturing partners. We do not receive compensation (either direct or indirect) from any of our partners, we just really like their work. 
                    </p>

                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold md:text-2xl dark:text-white"> Testing</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        We facilitate advanced testing on-site in our Long Beach facility. 
                        
                        <ul>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- <b>Functional</b>: HIL, SIL, Static, Dynamic, and Parametric</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- <b>Environmental</b>: Temperature, Humidity, and Mechanical Stress</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- <b>EMI/EMC</b>: Electromagnetic Interference/Compatibility </li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- <b>Lifecycle</b>: Stress and Accelerated Aging </li>
                        </ul>

                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        Our testing and verification partners enable us to take your product all the way through to production. Whether it be FCC/CE or something more exotic, we can prepare for and handle just about any certification testing process on your behalf for no additional charge.  
                    
                    </p>
                    <PrimaryArrowButton href="/services">View Our Services</PrimaryArrowButton>

                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl dark:text-white">Who Do We Work With?</h1>

                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        We are ready and more than willing to work with any individuals or companies in any domain
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        Our past clients are mainly small to medium business in the following domains:
                    </p>

                    <ul>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- Industrial/Automation</li>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- Biomedical Devices</li>
                        <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">- Consumer Electronics</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl dark:text-white">What is Our Guiding Philosophy?</h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                        <ol>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">1. <b>People over Profits</b>: We view our clients as people not potential revenue</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">2. <b>Efficiency</b>: We are passionate about doing more with less </li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">3. <b>Collaboration</b>: We work best when we work together</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">4. <b>Communication</b>: We stay connected with our clients and one another</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">5. <b>Discretion</b>: We value the privacy of our clients and their ideas </li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">6. <b>Ownership</b>: We take pride in our work</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">7. <b>Integrity</b>: We own our mistakes and admit when we are wrong</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">8. <b>Simplicity</b>: We strive for simplicity in our work</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">9. <b>Frugality</b>: We value value</li>
                            <li class="text-lg dark:text-white">10. <b>Do No Harm</b>: We do not develop weapons</li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>

                </div>
                <!-- End Content -->
            </div>

            <!-- End About -->
        </div>
    </Container>
</Layout>
